<p>John:</p>
<p>Getting set up with a login on the ticket system is easy. Here's how:</p>
<p>To use the ticketing system, you must first register yourself a login:</p>
<p>* point a browser at http://ticket.isaw.nyu.edu/<br />* below the picture of the building on the left-hand side, click "login"<br />* on the login dialog box, click "register"<br />* fill in the appropriate information and click the "register" button</p>
<p>On subsequent visits to the site, you will need to login, via the <br />"login" link on the left-hand side. Note that, in the login dialog, you <br />can select the "remember me" check-box so that you are automatically <br />logged in on subsequent visits.</p>
<p>Best,<br />Tom</p>